dct_title_s: Nord-Ostpreussens Südosten: Insterburg - Gumbinnen - Rominter Heide mit Detailkarte Hauptgestüt Trakhnen/ Dirk Bloch. (Recto)
dct_description_sm: Panel title. Legend, illustrations, and location map on recto. Map shows actual place names and historical German place names from 1938 to 1945. Russian place names are given in Cyrillic and Latin script. Index, location map, and ancillary map "Hauptgestüt Trakehnen und seine Vorwerke" on verso.
dct_subject_sm: Cities and towns—Prussia, East (Poland and Russia)—Maps
dcat_theme_sm: Cities and towns—Prussia, East (Poland and Russia)—Maps
